description:
The Haveli Collection by designer Poornima Jain, features a remarkable assembly of textiles and costumes that reveal the artistry behind human creativity. This Sasken exhibition offers a sneak peek into this exquisite collection.

The exhibition focuses on the journey from the earliest twisted fibers to finished garments, inviting us to view cloth as a manifestation of rhythm, logic, and human intelligence woven into form. Each piece tells a story of cultural heritage, where ancient techniques meet contemporary inspiration, and every thread connects us to the hands that shaped it.

&nbsp;
